** {F10266}Every value in SQLite has one of five fundamental datatypes:
**
** <ul>
** <li> 64-bit signed INTEGER
** <li> 64-bit IEEE floating pocint number
** <li> string
** <li> BLOB
** <li> NULL
** </ul> {END}
